{"_response_info":{"status":"ok"},"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/recover-debt-from-elsewhere-in-european-union.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/recover-debt-from-elsewhere-in-european-union","title":"Recover debt from elsewhere in the EU","format":"answer","updated_at":"2012-10-24T16:51:35+00:00","details":{"need_id":"B77","business_proposition":true,"description":"Debt recovery if you're owed money from people or businesses in another EU country - how to ask for a repayment","language":"en","body":"\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>If you’re owed money by someone in another EU country, you can recover the debt using internationally-recognised court forms.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>This is known as making a &lsquo;cross-border&rsquo; claim. You will have to pay a court fee.</p>\n\n<h2>If they admit owing the money</h2>\n\n<p>If the other person or business admits owing the money, you can make a <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://e-justice.europa.eu/content_european_payment_order-41-en.do\" title=\"European Payment Order\">European Payment Order.</a></p>\n\n<h2>If they deny owing the money</h2>\n\n<p>If they deny owing the money, and you&rsquo;re owed less than €2,000, you can use the <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://e-justice.europa.eu/content_small_claims-42-en.do\" title=\"European Small Claims Procedure\">European Small Claims procedure.</a></p>\n\n<p>For larger sums of money, you may have to use the national court system, and should get legal advice:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://legaladviserfinder.justice.gov.uk/AdviserSearch.do\" title=\"find a legal adviser\">find a legal adviser (England and Wales)</a></li>\n  <li><a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.lawscot.org.uk/wcm/lssservices/find_a_solicitor/Core/directory.aspx\" title=\"find a solicitor (Scotland)\">find a solicitor (Scotland)</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Find out more about <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://hmctsformfinder.justice.gov.uk/HMCTS/GetLeaflet.do?court_leaflets_id=1048\" title=\"making a cross-border claim in the EU\">making a cross-border claim in the EU.</a></p>\n","alternative_title":""},"tags":[{"title":"Court claims, debt and bankruptcy","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/tax%2Fcourt-claims-debt-bankruptcy.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes recovering debts, registering for bankruptcy and as a creditor","short_description":null,"type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=tax%2Fcourt-claims-debt-bankruptcy","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/tax/court-claims-debt-bankruptcy"},"parent":{"title":"Money and tax","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/tax.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes VAT, debt and inheritance tax","short_description":null,"type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=tax","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/tax"},"parent":null}},{"title":"Funding and debt","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/business%2Ffunding-debt.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes bankruptcy, business finance and recovering debt","short_description":null,"type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=business%2Ffunding-debt","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/business/funding-debt"},"parent":{"title":"Businesses and self-employed","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/business.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Information about starting up and running a business in the UK, including help if you're self employed or a sole trader.","short_description":null,"type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=business","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/business"},"parent":null}},{"title":"Business Link","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/businesslink.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":null,"short_description":null,"type":"legacy_source"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=businesslink","web_url"